---
description: Frontend-specific governance when UI code exists.
globs:
  - "src/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/**/*.jsx"
  - "app/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Frontend

- Components: PascalCase (`UserProfileCard.tsx`)
- Hooks: `useThing.ts`
- Prefer accessible, testable components.
- UI-only changes: typecheck, component tests, manual/visual check.
